		<td>
	





<P>It's entertainment, education and so much more. Here's where you get current on DTV, DVD, MP3, CD-R, HAVi, Avio and a host of other abbreviations that represent the cutting-edge of consumer technology. </P>
<P>Twenty-one sessions cover the newest digital advances in audio, personalized TV, flat panel TVs, video games and electronic books. Learn about home networking, copy protection, new delivery methods, what's happening in today's high-tech home and what's on the horizon. </P>



		
